  "author_association": "MEMBER",
  "body": "Closes https://github.com/coder/internal/issues/447.\r\n\r\nThe test was failing 30% of the time on Windows without the rounding applied by `dbtime`. `dbtime` was used on the timestamps inserted into the DB, but not within the query. Once using `dbtime` within the query there were no failures in 200 runs.",
